    "title": "Knowledge-Infused Multimodal Retrieval for Scientific Papers",
    "authors": [],
    "abstract": "This paper presents a knowledge-infused multimodal question answering system for scientific research papers, combining structured parsing, retrieval, and evidence attribution.",
